title: these should not fetch the same data (unless the user is baseline), but they do
pid: a10d0c50-58ab-4de2-9c9c-fa22d5fef46a
body: |2-
  user      = oio.readUserData (
    com.subsample,
    "report_" + unit + "." + com.strategy_year_suffix )

  baseline  = oio.readBaselineData (
    com.subsample,
    "report_" + unit + "." + com.strategy_year_suffix )
